    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Sometimes when you cast spells, unpredictable things happen. Tapping into the source of your chaotic power is usually helpful, but can also be violent and dangerous.</em></p><p></p><p>When you cast a spell of 1st level or higher, roll [[/r 1d6]]. If you roll a 5 or a 6, you trigger a wild surge, granting your spell an additional effect. The additional effect is not affected by your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.zH8SvVHZWJOkh0jB]{metamagic} features.</p><p></p><p>See our wild magic page for details on @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-rules.JournalEntry.FEMWrKEyIrd0s6BT.JournalEntryPage.VJrA212Hv3sI9yQv]{wild surges}.</p>",
